attributes.background:
I propose that all mullet hairstyles be phased out by the year 2010, by introducing a licencing restriction;
Persons with mullet hairstyles at the time of the new law being passed in parliament, shall be issued with a photo id/pass confirming that their hair has not been styled thus after the introduction of the new law, persons without said id/pass shall be detained and have the offending mullet removed.
The legal mullet id/pass carriers shall then grow-out/restyle their hair before a proposed and agreed expiry date not exceeding january 1st 2010.
